window.bookSummaryJSON = "In today's highly competitive business environment, you must know how to write in a clear and convincing way if you want to get ahead. This unique audio enables you to do so quickly and easily!<p>Business writing consultant Carol Gelderman provides simple techniques and practical examples to help you:</p><p></p><li>Organize key ideas and put them into logical order<br></li><li>Choose the right words and proper tone to get your points across<br></li><li>Avoid common spelling and grammatical mistakes<br></li><li>Brush up on punctuation to make your message inviting to read and easy to understand<br></li><li>Correct flaws in emphasis and style, such as awkward transitions and misplaced modifiers<br></li><li>Edit your writing to eliminate unnecessary words or phrases and ensure clarity</li>"; 
